ru.cos.sim.road.objects
Interface RoadObject

All Superinterfaces:
Point
All Known Subinterfaces:
RectangleRoadObject, Vehicle
All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractRectangleRoadObject, AbstractRoadObject, AbstractVehicle, BlockRoadObject, EndOfLanePoint, IntersectionPoint, NodeForkPoint, NodeJoinPoint, NoSpeedLimitSign, Obstacle, RegularVehicle, Sign, SpeedLimitSign, StartOfLanePoint, StopLine, TrafficLight
public interface RoadObject
extends Point

Object on the road which location can be described by triplet of lengthy, position and shift. Shift - it is the distance from the object to the lengthy's curve. Shift is measured in meters and is positive if it is on the right from lengthy, negative if on the left.

Author:
zroslaw
